COUNTRY CLASS
List of countries containing each country and its population percentage

~~Participating Method~~
Print a list of all countries participating
Ask if they would like to remove any countries from participating
	if yes
		while they're still wanting to remove countries
		ask the user the name of the country they want to remove
		remove the corresponding country from the list

